description: Listed only by Irwin, who says: An 8' manual Chorus Reed of the Trumpet species, sounding with some degree of blatancy, a free-toned vibration, and great loudness. It is a Solo or Fanfare Organ stop.
examplesDescription: Trumpet Royal 8', Solo; Convention Hall, Atlantic City, New Jersey, USA; Midmer-Losh 1929-32.
